{"talk":{"id":10666,"name":"Howard C. Stevenson: How to resolve racially stressful situations","description":"If we hope to heal the racial tensions that threaten to tear the fabric of society apart, we're going to need the skills to openly express ourselves in racially stressful situations. Through racial literacy -- the ability to read, recast and resolve these situations -- psychologist Howard C. Stevenson helps children and parents reduce and manage stress and trauma. In this inspiring, quietly awesome talk, learn more about how this approach to decoding racial threat can help youth build confidence and stand up for themselves in productive ways.","slug":"howard_c_stevenson_how_to_resolve_racially_stressful_situations","recorded_at":"2017-11-01 00:00:00","published_at":"2018-02-24 15:38:00","updated_at":"2020-09-28 21:44:20","viewed_count":1848555,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":483,"name":"TEDMED 2017"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/3d8e44d629d2a528bdc5f163a31196496241bb08_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/3d8e44d629d2a528bdc5f163a31196496241bb08_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/3d8e44d629d2a528bdc5f163a31196496241bb08_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/3d8e44d629d2a528bdc5f163a31196496241bb08_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/93ad140a909956ff360836fc2631465f370ab695_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/HowardStevenson_2017P-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":8669463,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/HowardStevenson_2017P-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":24068632,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/HowardStevens